          <div class="faq-answer">Some do, some don't. theStacc includes SEO optimization in every article — keyword targeting, meta descriptions, internal links, and header structure. Surfer SEO is the best standalone optimization layer. Buffer and CoSchedule handle scheduling but have limited SEO features. For small teams, a tool that bundles content production and SEO is more efficient than buying separate tools for each function.</div>
